question: Arya, Quentyn and Doran ^__^.
answer:
Arya:

general opinion: fall in a hole and die | don’t like them | eh | they’re fine I guess | like them! | love them | actual love of my life
hotness level: get away from me | meh | neutral (she’s a child) | theoretically hot but not my type | pretty hot | gorgeous! | 10/10 would bang
hogwarts house: gryffindor | slytherin | ravenclaw | hufflepuff
best quality: Brave. Tough. Smart. Survivor
worst quality: Impulsiveness which is not surprising given her age. 
ship them with: No one on account of her age
brotp them with: Gendry. Hot Pie
needs to stay away from: War. 
misc. thoughts: Too young for people to go ‘badass!’ instead of ‘that’s very concerning’

Quentyn:

general opinion: fall in a hole and die | don’t like them | eh | they’re fine I guess | like them! | love them | actual love of my life
hotness level: get away from me | meh | neutral | theoretically hot but not my type | pretty hot | gorgeous! | 10/10 would bang
hogwarts house: gryffindor | slytherin | ravenclaw | hufflepuff
best quality: A good person. Survived a lot of horror. Wants to honor his friends. One of the few boys in the story who isn’t a fuckboy. Didn’t think too highly of himself when it came dragons. Wanted to make his dad proud. Tragic. Sweet child.
worst quality: Shyness. If he had been firmer and more confident he would have lived :(
ship them with: No one. I don’t know much about the girl he wanted so…
brotp them with: Cletus. Gerris. Archibald
needs to stay away from: Dragons
misc. thoughts: He didn’t need to die like that. Stop using the only prominent brown characters to violently deconstruct beloved fantasy tropes George!

Doran:

general opinion: fall in a hole and die | don’t like them | eh | they’re fine I guess | like them! | love them | actual love of my life
hotness level: get away from me | meh | neutral | theoretically hot but not my type | pretty hot | gorgeous! | 10/10 would bang
hogwarts house: gryffindor | slytherin | ravenclaw | hufflepuff
best quality: Cautious. Smart. Actually cares about the damage of war. Loves his family. Doesn’t hurt little children. 
worst quality: Too secretive. Destroyed his life trying to avenge is his siblings :(. That time he subjected his daughter to solitary confinement. 
ship them with: Mellario. Open to Rhaella
brotp them with: Oberyn. Areo. Elia.
needs to stay away from: Keeping his mouth shut too much. Targaryens.
misc. thoughts: Ignore this fandom’s racist tendencies of putting him down while flicking their clits to Tywin and Roose. Doran is good.

summary: Hey there, can anyone point me to places in the text where Sansa bullied Arya and vice versa (books not the show)? I want to...
body: Hey there, can anyone point me to places in the text where Sansa bullied Arya and vice versa (books not the show)? I want to continue being mad about the fact that D&D pitted these two sisters who loved each other and miss each other against each other instead of having them work together against Littlefinger, but either Sansa was a lot worse than I remember, Arya was a lot worse than I remember, or there are a lot of salty antis in both tags.
